# Patterns apply everywhere — root and nested cases (foo/, bar/, ...)

# Build output (dot-prefixed so it stays hidden in editor file trees)
**/.dist/
**/dist/

# Python
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/.pytest_cache/

# Secrets — never commit
**/.env
.dev.vars

# Planning / scratch — local only
**/docs/
**/tmp/
**/tmp/*.png

# Committed screenshots live under assets/ — see README.md.

# Cloudflare Wrangler
**/.wrangler/
**/node_modules/

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
